# Creatoe Deployment Sync

## Current Deployment State

- **GitHub Repo:** https://github.com/kartavyasimpplifit/creatoe (unified - backend + frontend)
- **Frontend (Vercel):** https://frontend-eta-five-22.vercel.app
- **Vercel Project:** kartavya-atris-projects/frontend
- **Backend runs locally** at http://localhost:8000, tunneled via Cloudflare

## Git + Deploy Commands (PATH setup required every session)

```powershell
$env:PATH = "C:\Program Files\GitHub CLI;" + "C:\Program Files\Git\cmd;" + $env:PATH
$env:GH_TOKEN = (gh auth token 2>$null)
cd "c:\Graph Ai"
git remote set-url origin "https://x-access-token:$env:GH_TOKEN@github.com/kartavyasimpplifit/creatoe.git"
```

## After ANY code change

1. Commit to the unified repo: `cd "c:\Graph Ai"; git add -A; git commit -m "msg"; git push origin master`
   NOTE: If push hangs, use token-based URL: `git remote set-url origin "https://x-access-token:$(gh auth token)@github.com/kartavyasimpplifit/creatoe.git"`
2. If frontend changed: `cd frontend; npx vercel --yes --prod`
3. If backend changed: restart uvicorn + restart tunnel

## After backend URL changes

1. `cd frontend; npx vercel env rm NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL production --yes`
2. `echo "NEW_URL" | npx vercel env add NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL production`
3. `npx vercel --yes --prod`
4. Update `frontend/.env.local` for local dev

## Design System (TikTok-style)

- Background: #000000, Cards: #161616, Accent: #818cf8
